      <title>“末日博士”诺里尔·鲁比尼 (Nouriel Roubini) 正考虑推出其首只 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/-dr-doom-nouriel-roubini-is-looking-to-launch-his-first-etf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家诺里尔鲁比尼 (Nouriel Roubini) 因在 2008 年金融危机前发出灾难警告而获得了“末日博士”的绰号，他有望成为最新一位在价值 9.4 万亿美元的 ETF 领域崭露头角的华尔街资深人士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/-dr-doom-nouriel-roubini-is-looking-to-launch-his-first-etf</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
